Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:01:59.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:04.29,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It actually happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:18.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:24.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:32.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still happy even if it's from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako went to get the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:50.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is December 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The day of the closing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:59.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was crazy yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:01.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:04.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She showed up for the second half of the party yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:15.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida handed her the mic, she sang one song and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:21.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And is it just me, or did she come with Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:26.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.27,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:38.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya lost to me in a game yesterday, so he had to wait for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:41.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako didn't know where the second half of the party was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:45.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:47.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:51.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still tasty stuff like Valentine's Day coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you ruin it with your antics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this bad feeling I'm getting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:03.41,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Sawako isn't even there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:08.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She might go on about\N “Kazehaya's reputation” and stuff again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They responded!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a belly warmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:42.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it stitch by stitch, thinking of my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:54.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally swapped it with what I was going to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:05:01.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, could you give it to your dad or mom or grandpa—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:04.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can have it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably won't even wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But he took it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:30.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he won't wear the cap either, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:31.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it with different feelings, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing pretty hard today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the closing ceremony today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.41,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Even snappier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Yano-chin, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cold hasn't gotten to you at all, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:12.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, the closing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:16.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess winter break starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:20.27,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get a bit lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:27.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for? Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:34.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zen! It's Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:35.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So here's the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:44.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be running my wife's family's brewery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So today's my last day teaching here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:53.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought something bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:07:02.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, the brewery's doing great, and things are going well with my in-laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a gold-digger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arai-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:11.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your farewell party? Let's have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:16.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but I have to go home right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget the time we had together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:26.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have a “worship your new teacher, Pin” party then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:35.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's line up in the hallway for the closing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Single file!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So much has happened—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:59.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute even when she's making faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:02.77,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,—this second semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter break is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:14.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll see you in good health next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:19.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,There was really so much that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Some painful things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:56.41,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but so many more happy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:10.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kuronuma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:15.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, she's an exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:22.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't look any different,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:30.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but so much of what I thought about and experienced was new to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:33.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, winter break tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:37.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go eat somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:45.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, let's go karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just went yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:52.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't see him after this, until the third semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:07.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:12.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.53,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:18.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Something short, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Happy new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:45.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,See you next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:52.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, your dad's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you set up e-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:58.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't read the whole manual yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to read the whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What address do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:13.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it long so that you don't get spammed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:16.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Name, birthday, stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that'll help fix the misunderstandings too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:30.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, your birthday's on New Year's Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:42.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan, Ayane-chan, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:48.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we could meet over the winter holiday too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:57.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're {\i1}really{\i0} bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:04.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, of course we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:08.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me, why would you bring that up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get in contact easier now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:20.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to wait until the third semester!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:27.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always go to the shrine with Ryu on New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:30.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys want to join us this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see everyone on New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:38.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:45.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'll check.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:47.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:52.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Chizu-chan and Ayane-chan? Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:55.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Dad when he gets home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:59.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He feels bad about yesterday. He won't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it that bad yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:12.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to see them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,on New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.27,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,On my 16th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to be with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:23.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have Kazehaya's phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:27.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it when I met him yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you called him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:44.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it'll be just Chizu, Ryu, you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:52.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but if you want to see Kazehaya, you better invite him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Invite him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:14:01.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better call him now, or he'll have different plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:04.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not forcing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just if you want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:16.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't call him now, I won't see him until the third semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:23.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know his email address.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:25.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:29.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? It's Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? It's Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:35.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's Eve Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:44.75,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm getting nervous too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:48.86,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be nice if I can see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:53.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Go me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:18.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's me, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:27.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to come to the New Year's Festival at the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be Chizu-chan, Ayane-chan, Sanada-kun and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:36.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you're bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:37.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:43.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida, Yano, Ryu and you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:46.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he's looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:59.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:07.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,On my birthday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:35.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Time flies, and it's December 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:42.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't Chizu-chan and Ayane-chan coming soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:46.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, it's not good to make your friends wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:51.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wear the poncho you got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:56.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's Eve Festival with your friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:17:06.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Chizu-chan and Ayane-chan are friends, but Sanada-kun and Kazehaya-kun... are they my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.38,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:24.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get my coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:27.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, can we come up to your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:29.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:32.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:40.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:47.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hardly tell you're wearing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:18:00.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wished you were cute when you met Kurumi, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:05.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about why you want to be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:08.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost done here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:12.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from Yano-chin and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:19.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hairpin looks good on you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:33.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:42.24,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to ruin their efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:45.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's even scarier with make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:51.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:56.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so, so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:19:03.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So many good things happened since I met you two this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:09.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pretty close to where we're supposed to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:12.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thinking, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:16.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:21.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun with Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:23.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:28.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu's not coming either, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a status report later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:34.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so serious? You're the one that invited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:18.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why Chizu-chan and Ayane-chan wanted to make me as cute as they could.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:21.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:23.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Yoshida and Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:26.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:31.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither is Sanada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I disappointed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.43,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.41,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He might leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:04.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,December 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:16.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty minutes until the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:32.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words woven
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:35.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on a night lit by snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:38.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:41.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
